OL,3,CCoroner suspends investigation into
OL,4,Cice hockey tragedy
OL,6,FA coroner examining the death of ice
OL,7,Fhockey player Adam Johnson has
OL,8,Fsuspended her investigation as police
OL,9,Finquiries continue.
OL,11,FJohnson was fatally injured when he
OL,12,Fwas struck in the neck by an
OL,13,Fopponent's skate during a match at
OL,14,FSheffield's Utilita Arena.
OL,16,FThe 29-year-old American, who was
OL,17,Fplaying for Nottingham Panthers
OL,18,Fagainst Sheffield Steelers, died in
OL,19,Fhospital on 28 October last year.
