OL,6,FThe incident, witnessed by thousands
OL,7,Fof fans inside the stadium, shocked
OL,8,Fthe ice hockey world.
OL,10,FSheffield's senior coroner Tanyka
OL,11,FRawden opened an inquest into Mr
OL,12,FJohnson's death last year. South
OL,13,FYorkshire Police later arrested a man
OL,14,Fon suspicion of manslaughter.
