OL,3,CCoroner suspends investigation into
OL,4,Cice hockey tragedy
OL,6,FFollowing a review of the case by Ms
OL,7,FRawden on Friday, her office confirmed
OL,8,Fthe suspension of her investigation.
OL,10,FIt said the suspension would last
OL,11,Funtil July unless South Yorkshire
OL,12,FPolice dropped its investigation.
