OL,3,CCoroner suspends investigation into
OL,4,Cice hockey tragedy
OL,6,FIn a statement on Friday, Ms Rawden's
OL,7,Foffice said: "If South Yorkshire
OL,8,FPolice determine before July 26 2024
OL,9,Fthat no person will be charged with a
OL,10,Fhomicide offence involving the death
OL,11,Fof the deceased, the coroner will
OL,12,Fresume her investigation upon
OL,13,Freceiving notification of that
OL,14,Fdecision."
OL,16,FAfter opening the inquest Ms Rawden
OL,17,Fissued a Prevention of Future Deaths
OL,18,FReport to Ice Hockey UK and the
OL,19,FEnglish Ice Hockey Association (EIHA)
OL,20,Fabout the use of neck guards in the
OL,21,Fsport.
