OL,6,FIn the report, the coroner said she
OL,7,Fwas "sufficiently concerned that
OL,8,Fdeaths may occur in the future if neck
OL,9,Fguards or protectors are not worn",
OL,10,Fwith the bodies given 56 days to say
OL,11,Fwhat action had been taken or why they
OL,12,Fhad taken no action.
OL,14,FThe EIHA said neck guards would become
OL,15,Fmandatory from 2024 but the Elite
OL,16,FLeague, in which the Nottingham
OL,17,FPanthers and Sheffield Steelers
OL,18,Fcompete, is not under its control.
