OL,6,FThe Elite Ice Hockey League said it
OL,7,Fwill not make the use of neck guards
OL,8,Fmandatory but would "strongly
OL,9,Fencourage" players and officials to
OL,10,Fwear them.
OL,12,FThe arrested man was bailed by police
OL,13,Fin November to a date in the new year.
